{"id":232884321,"title":"無名","content":"今晚  我還是夢見了妳\n在當年相遇的那個街道上\n再次相遇\n沒有過多的話\n只有微笑點頭\n\n然而\n我卻不滿足於現狀\n就這樣緊緊抱著妳\n\n妳由震驚轉為激動\n用力抓著我的衣服\n眼淚不停流\n直到沾濕了袖\n\n「你不離。」「我不棄。」","excerpt":"今晚  我還是夢見了妳，在當年相遇的那個街道上，再次相遇，沒有過多的話，只有微笑點頭，然而，我卻不滿足於現狀，就這樣緊緊抱著妳，妳由震驚轉為激動，用力抓著我的衣服，眼淚不停流，直到沾濕了袖，「你不離。","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f8acd3e6-17e9-4d9d-bc7c-bf24d94c2ad1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-13T12:15:09.809Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-13T12:15:09.809Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":0,"tags":[],"topics":["新詩","隨筆","心情"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"詩文","forumAlias":"literature","school":"思爾天想","department":"m.e3952","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[],"postAvatar":""}